      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/holiday-gift-programs-that-benefit-nonprofits.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-14988\" alt=\"holiday gift programs that benefit nonprofits\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/holiday-gift-programs-that-benefit-nonprofits-300x298.jpg?resize=300%2C298\" width=\"300\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/holiday-gift-programs-that-benefit-nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C298&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/holiday-gift-programs-that-benefit-nonprofits.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/holiday-gift-programs-that-benefit-nonprofits.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/holiday-gift-programs-that-benefit-nonprofits.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/holiday-gift-programs-that-benefit-nonprofits.jpg?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>As follow-up to\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2013/10/27/22-online-gift-stores-that-benefit-nonprofits/\">29 Online Gift Stores That Benefit Nonprofits</a>, below are 19 nonprofits that are offering symbolic gifts and adoptions this holiday season. These gift programs are ideal for socially and environmentally conscious holiday shoppers that would prefer their spending directly empower nonprofits. They also make excellent gifts for activists and advocates of global development, environmental conservation, and wildlife protection. Assured to make an impact, the gift programs listed below are meaningful gifts for family and friends of any age.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. American Rivers Gifts</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.americanrivers.org/store/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14951\" alt=\"shop-now4\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/shop-now4.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.americanrivers.org/store/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14971\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"American Rivers\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/American-Rivers.png?resize=600%2C275\" width=\"600\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/American-Rivers.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/American-Rivers.png?resize=300%2C137&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. charity: water Donation Cards</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://store.charitywater.org/products/gift-card\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14951\" alt=\"shop-now4\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/shop-now4.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://store.charitywater.org/products/gift-card\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14982\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Charity Water\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Charity-Water.png?resize=600%2C330\" width=\"600\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Charity-Water.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Charity-Water.png?resize=300%2C165&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. David Shelrick Wildlife Trust Orphan Adoptions</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.sheldrickwildlifetrust.org/asp/fostering.asp\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14951\" alt=\"shop-now4\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/shop-now4.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.sheldrickwildlifetrust.org/asp/fostering.asp\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14977\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"DWST\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/DWST.png?resize=600%2C347\" width=\"600\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/DWST.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/DWST.png?resize=300%2C173&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Defenders of Wildlife Adoptions</h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://secure.defenders.org/site/SPageServer?pagename=wagc_homepage&amp;s_src=3WEW1300XXXXX&amp;s_subsrc=110312_right_side_home\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14951\" alt=\"shop-now4\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/shop-now4.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://secure.defenders.org/site/SPageServer?pagename=w